alpha, right?

01:06:13.210 --> 01:06:14.850 align:middle line:90%
Have put a lot on my plate.

01:06:14.850 --> 01:06:18.310 align:middle line:84%
I literally have so many
projects going on at one time.

01:06:18.310 --> 01:06:23.100 align:middle line:84%
I'm a very structured,
Virgo brained, logical side.

01:06:23.100 --> 01:06:27.630 align:middle line:84%
And my question is,
how can I kind of help

01:06:27.630 --> 01:06:29.820 align:middle line:84%
