Personally, you can use
a lot of technologies.

01:08:57.430 --> 01:08:59.229 align:middle line:84%
You can use a lot
of pharmacologies.

01:08:59.229 --> 01:09:01.479 align:middle line:84%
I don't like to depend
on either, which is not

01:09:01.479 --> 01:09:03.250 align:middle line:90%
