01:09:03.250 --> 01:09:06.096 align:middle line:84%
It's that I want to be
able to be at my best

01:09:06.096 --> 01:09:07.304 align:middle line:90%
when I need to be at my best.

01:09:07.304 --> 01:09:08.529 align:middle line:90%
I don't want to have to--

01:09:08.529 --> 01:09:12.970 align:middle line:84%
so I like the psychological
triggers-- novelty, complexity,

01:09:12.970 --> 01:09:13.899 align:middle line:90%
unpredictability.

01:09:13.899 --> 01:09:14.740 align:middle line:90%
Jason is not wrong.

01:09:14.740 --> 01:09:16.750 align:middle line:90%
They spike dopamine 400%.

