This is Robert Sapolsky's
work at Stanford.

01:09:19.990 --> 01:09:22.540 align:middle line:84%
And so those are great,
great flow triggers.

01:09:22.540 --> 01:09:25.330 align:middle line:90%
Risk is a great flow trigger.

01:09:25.330 --> 01:09:27.460 align:middle line:84%
From your description
of yourself,

01:09:27.460 --> 01:09:30.223 align:middle line:84%
