01:10:07.475 --> 01:10:08.850 align:middle line:84%
You've got to go
slow to go fast.

01:10:08.850 --> 01:10:13.300 align:middle line:84%
So you think if you take two
days off to go do whatever

01:10:13.300 --> 01:10:16.060 align:middle line:84%
