01:10:17.620 --> 01:10:20.238 align:middle line:84%
You're 500% more
productive in flow.

01:10:20.238 --> 01:10:22.030 align:middle line:84%
This is not just a
number I'm throwing out.

01:10:22.030 --> 01:10:24.880 align:middle line:84%
McKinsey did a study of
top executives in flow.

01:10:24.880 --> 01:10:27.495 align:middle line:84%
