so take it or leave it.

01:10:27.495 --> 01:10:29.620 align:middle line:84%
But across the board-- and
a huge swatch of people.

01:10:29.620 --> 01:10:31.352 align:middle line:84%
They reported being
5X more productive.

01:10:31.352 --> 01:10:32.185 align:middle line:90%
Put that in context.

01:10:32.185 --> 01:10:33.750 align:middle line:90%
It's 500% more productive.

01:10:33.750 --> 01:10:35.520 align:middle line:84%
It means you got
to work on Monday.

01:10:35.520 --> 01:10:36.580 align:middle line:90%
Spend it in flow state.

01:10:36.580 --> 01:10:38.500 align:middle line:84%
You can take Tuesday
through Friday off,

01:10:38.500 --> 01:10:40.540 align:middle line:84%
and you're going to get as
much done as your steady state

01:10:40.540 --> 01:10:41.340 align:middle line:90%
peers.

01:10:41.340 --> 01:10:43.130 align:middle line:90%
It's a massive acceleration.

01:10:43.130 --> 01:10:47.380 align:middle line:84%
So even though it feels
like you're wasting time,

01:10:47.380 --> 01:10:49.342 align:middle line:90%
