01:10:49.342 --> 01:10:50.818 align:middle line:90%
>> Wow.

01:10:50.818 --> 01:10:54.262 align:middle line:84%
Using flow every day-- since
you're a structured creative,

01:10:54.262 --> 01:10:55.740 align:middle line:90%
you write every day, right?

01:10:55.740 --> 01:10:57.010 align:middle line:90%
