01:11:54.340 --> 01:11:55.757 align:middle line:84%
Yeah, that produced
the most flow.

01:11:55.757 --> 01:11:59.250 align:middle line:84%
So there's literally--
as far as I can tell,

01:11:59.250 --> 01:12:01.960 align:middle line:84%
that's just a fast
metabolism and energy there.

01:12:01.960 --> 01:12:03.510 align:middle line:84%
So I don't see any
correlation there.

01:12:03.510 --> 01:12:05.876 align:middle line:90%
But, yeah, does that help?

01:12:05.876 --> 01:12:06.676 align:middle line:90%
>> Yeah.

