coffee, some emails,

01:12:34.820 --> 01:12:38.000 align:middle line:90%
get this shit done, so to speak.

01:12:38.000 --> 01:12:42.490 align:middle line:84%
And then usually by noon or
1 o'clock, I'm ready to flip.

01:12:42.490 --> 01:12:45.543 align:middle line:84%
So it's like I go from morning
and convergent thinking.

01:12:45.543 --> 01:12:47.960 align:middle line:84%
