want like divergent thinking.

01:12:47.960 --> 01:12:49.490 align:middle line:84%
I want to go for
a hike, and I want

01:12:49.490 --> 01:12:52.880 align:middle line:84%
to have unexpected insights,
and et cetera, et cetera.

01:12:52.880 --> 01:12:54.590 align:middle line:90%
But I tend to be--

01:12:54.590 --> 01:12:56.750 align:middle line:84%
I tend to purposefully
treat myself

01:12:56.750 --> 01:13:00.620 align:middle line:90%
in a very calm matter on a day--

01:13:00.620 --> 01:13:04.100 align:middle line:84%
calm manner-- sorry--
on a day-to-day basis.

01:13:04.100 --> 01:13:06.010 align:middle line:90%
Because it's kind of like--

01:13:06.010 --> 01:13:09.410 align:middle line:84%
