people draining.

01:13:42.120 --> 01:13:45.330 align:middle line:90%
No offense to them.

01:13:45.330 --> 01:13:47.070 align:middle line:90%
It's just me.

01:13:47.070 --> 01:13:49.560 align:middle line:84%
I just-- I want to
save my engagement

01:13:49.560 --> 01:13:52.300 align:middle line:90%
for the deeply meaningful.

01:13:52.300 --> 01:13:59.442 align:middle line:84%
And I will build my whole life
