01:14:56.760 --> 01:14:59.940 align:middle line:84%
I mean, everybody at their
absolute best working together.

01:14:59.940 --> 01:15:01.460 align:middle line:90%
And that means flow, right?

01:15:01.460 --> 01:15:02.900 align:middle line:84%
So I think we're
all going to have

01:15:02.900 --> 01:15:04.192 align:middle line:90%
