01:17:00.620 --> 01:17:02.280 align:middle line:84%
There are three
levels of happiness.

01:17:02.280 --> 01:17:04.540 align:middle line:84%
There's happiness--
how you feel right now.

01:17:04.540 --> 01:17:06.430 align:middle line:84%
And there's not a whole
lot you can do there.

01:17:06.430 --> 01:17:08.430 align:middle line:84%
There's a little bit of
techniques you can have.

01:17:08.430 --> 01:17:09.903 align:middle line:90%
But pretty much it's--

01:17:09.903 --> 01:17:10.820 align:middle line:90%
a lot of it's genetic.

01:17:10.820 --> 01:17:11.660 align:middle line:90%
A lot of it's nature, nurture.

01:17:11.660 --> 01:17:12.200 align:middle line:90%
You can't do much.

01:17:12.200 --> 01:17:14.900 align:middle line:84%
Second level is what they call
enjoyment, which is literally

01:17:14.900 --> 01:17:16.970 align:middle line:90%
a high flow life, right?

01:17:16.970 --> 01:17:19.400 align:middle line:84%
And the third level
is a meaningful life.

01:17:19.400 --> 01:17:22.490 align:middle line:84%
And that's high flow,
plus purpose, basically.

01:17:22.490 --> 01:17:25.160 align:middle line:84%
So what we know is the
people who score off

01:17:25.160 --> 01:17:27.620 align:middle line:84%
